<div class="nbunit" id="a11Apr1937"><font color="red">11 April 1937</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Giorgio Joyce): Sunday &hellip; I have seen Vogt at last. He found my sight much improved &hellip; perhaps we will be able to leave at the end of the week </div>
